    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable vehicle that's ready to work for you? This car is in fair condition and shows some honest character from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, dependable choice for your daily needs! It's a fantastic opportunity to get behind the wheel of a functional ride at a price that fits your budget perfectly. Come see the value for yourself!",
