      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Maintained to a fastidious standard, the exterior retains a showroom-grade luster, while the interior remains entirely unblemished. Every mechanical component has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure peak performance and absolute reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 45800.0,
